Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.67,0:00:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 吃飯了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.98,0:00:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在吃了 在吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.48,0:00:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夢 那個餌料難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.49,0:00:16.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的 不會過甜的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.40,0:00:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是甜的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.77,0:00:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃吧 文太
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.70,0:00:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊呀 這傢伙是只花貓 難道不是母的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.06,0:00:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是母的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.24,0:00:26.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就給它起一個更女孩子點的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.63,0:00:28.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如 加奈 呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.36,0:00:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這得取得本人的同意啊 雖然絕對不會同意的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.50,0:00:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為看嘛 這孩子一臉文靜相
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.85,0:00:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？代理已經出門了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.90,0:00:43.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.75,0:00:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 本想一起去的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.76,0:00:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是去久違的學校 現在正幹勁十足的進行擴張吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.83,0:00:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擴張？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.46,0:00:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,角鳥？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:00:57.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各腸？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.31,0:00:58.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.10,0:00:58.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.93,0:01:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 已經這個點了 遲到了 遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.62,0:01:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遲到了 遲到了 遲到了 遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.87,0:01:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈醬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.77,0:01:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.77,0:01:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上學的日子的早餐吃麵包就可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.71,0:01:19.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 好的 我知道了 那麼我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.41,0:01:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.77,0:01:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此一來 就能在新學期看到咬著麵包的少女的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.63,0:01:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遲到了 遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.06,0:01:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…的畫面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.68,0:01:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真期待
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.05,0:01:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別大清早就開始喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.65,0:01:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婆婆 今天是暑假中的返校日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.50,0:01:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是入住專賣所以來第一次上學
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.17,0:01:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然擔心會不會迷路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.53,0:01:54.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是多虧了送報的經驗 甚至還發現了近路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.70,0:02:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婆婆 我覺得我能把送報娘做好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.54,0:03:37.32,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(455,320)}{\fad(500,0)}第一次的、微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.97,0:03:35.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.61,0:03:40.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭啦 健君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.54,0:03:44.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 上次從健君媽媽那裡得到的點心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.58,0:03:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底在哪家店裡買的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:49.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是媽媽親手做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:56.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的麼 太好吃了 我還以為是哪家有名的點心店做的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.91,0:04:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我跟媽媽說再給妳做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.87,0:04:02.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝啦 健君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:04.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.67,0:04:08.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咲妃醬 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:12.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽我說哦 我媽媽說想訂咲妃醬家的報紙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.65,0:04:18.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真的麼 那麼放學之後請讓我跟妳媽媽談談吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.12,0:04:20.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.14,0:04:24.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊 我也跟媽媽說好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.59,0:04:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.02,0:04:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕上了 趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.70,0:04:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.92,0:04:41.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們聽說了哦 妳婆婆的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.87,0:04:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:44.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒有什麼我們能做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.69,0:04:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管什麼儘管吩咐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.62,0:04:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嗯 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.34,0:04:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打鈴了 大家請就座
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:57.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 一會說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.97,0:04:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:04:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打起精神來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.54,0:05:00.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.24,0:05:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 大家請注意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.25,0:05:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天雖然是臨時上課 但要為大家介紹一位轉校生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.49,0:05:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從第二學期開始就要在我們學校上學的久地院美華同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:21.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久地院 請簡單介紹下自己
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.23,0:05:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了 我和你們不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.03,0:05:36.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不要隨隨便便跟我說話 明白了麼 你們這些平民
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？那是什麼性格
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.66,0:05:40.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那發言行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.13,0:05:41.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該拿這孩子怎麼辦好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.56,0:05:42.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如說 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.17,0:05:49.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是妳啊 中町加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是熟人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:52.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:53.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.69,0:05:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來只是偶然在附近見過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.32,0:06:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 所以比起說是熟人不如說是夥伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夥伴？只是偶然見面就？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:05.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.96,0:06:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說傻話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.69,0:06:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰跟像妳這樣的平民是夥伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.96,0:06:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.51,0:06:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋…朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.20,0:06:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我不需要平民做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.45,0:06:24.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶吶 久地院同學穿的校服是白薔薇學院的制服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.00,0:06:32.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個超有錢人上的學校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.31,0:06:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是倒是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.34,0:06:37.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是為什麼呢 好不容易在白薔薇學院上學了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.60,0:06:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻為什麼來我們學校呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼一說…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.68,0:06:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過去在有錢人的學校上學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轉到了經濟實惠的都立中學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.53,0:06:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.37,0:06:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.10,0:06:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(180,30)}{\fs25}{\fad(500,500)}需要被關心…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.19,0:06:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是我們中校的校服 我們的也很好看吧 吶吶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們到底想說什麼 把我當笨蛋麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:06:59.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:02.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起這個 加奈 帶她參觀下校內如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.22,0:07:07.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哦 妳還完全不知道學校裡面的樣子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.18,0:07:11.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 我從來都不向平民打聽問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.06,0:07:16.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈才是 要依靠我也行哦 問什麼都行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.77,0:07:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.84,0:07:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼快就要問了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.65,0:07:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.73,0:07:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳的名字是什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:29.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳這個無禮的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們去買東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.25,0:07:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拜託買的酒可別忘了買哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:37.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道咯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.34,0:07:45.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.51,0:07:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來 怎麼樣？久違的學校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我是個無禮的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.98,0:07:55.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭啦 意義不明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:58.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈醬真是的 太可愛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:03.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別動不動就發情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.39,0:08:06.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啦 那麼 就一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.12,0:08:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是 又發情了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.77,0:08:12.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要八次 八次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.37,0:08:13.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回數怎麼還增加啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八次都不行啊 那還有五次 再來五次就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們到底在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.71,0:08:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳問做什麼 一直不就是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:28.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是問妳這個 是問你們把門開著在搞些什麼名堂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被人家知道我們這有變態在 合同會減少的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.26,0:08:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來 收穫如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:37.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還用說 理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.47,0:08:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是代理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:40.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擴張業務辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 這個「擴張」到底是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.01,0:08:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天早上也聽到了這詞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:49.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勸誘的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:56.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勸誘？ 是訂報紙的勸誘嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.06,0:09:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,報社還能勸誘別人訂其他東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 但是在小學裡進行勸誘…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.88,0:09:08.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說 小學裡的學生都是這附近的孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.20,0:09:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和他們搞好關係的話 從而就能跟他們的父母親近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話 要和他們簽訂報合同也容易了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.09,0:09:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要做到這種地步嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.89,0:09:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是基本 基本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.79,0:09:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然加奈已經來我們這干了 就要精通完美的擴張笑容哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.36,0:09:26.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擴張笑容？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.94,0:09:29.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 仔細看好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.75,0:09:38.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 妳試試
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.74,0:09:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.74,0:09:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要做了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.66,0:09:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的眼鏡…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.16,0:09:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Smile
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.05,0:09:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這感覺該怎麼說呢 好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.23,0:09:58.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 不應該強迫妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.54,0:10:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行？ 我不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,微笑 這樣嗎 還是這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.37,0:10:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.42,0:10:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是不行麼 好奇怪 哪個地方沒做對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.11,0:10:33.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢 普通的微笑是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.28,0:10:35.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:38.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混沌顏 是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.64,0:10:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 多做練習的話肯定會變好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以加奈…別真哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:46.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.71,0:10:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,練習啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.89,0:10:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久地院同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:11:00.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是加奈麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.52,0:11:02.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 又迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.99,0:11:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳才迷路了 妳這個無禮的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 那是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:14.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…是那個 偶然從附近經過順便到妳這來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:18.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈 有客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.95,0:11:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 這位是久地院美華同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.54,0:11:23.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在花日報社…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.52,0:11:28.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花日？ 妳是花日報社的間諜？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:31.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳憑什麼隨意做出這種錯誤的論斷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.84,0:11:34.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我奉命出來進行擴張 順便…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:37.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳說擴張？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.57,0:11:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是勸誘別人訂報紙的意思哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我當然知道 比起那個 妳給我過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久地院同學 稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.79,0:11:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.32,0:11:51.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈 妳給我聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.53,0:11:56.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花日報紙在上個月訂報時間快結束時搶走了我們15家生意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:59.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去問了理由 居然是「米」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.00,0:12:03.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「訂他們的報紙的話 就附送大米哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:05.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.52,0:12:09.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們又是不米店！是報社啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.14,0:12:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒米的話吃紙不就好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綜上所述 加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.81,0:12:18.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳也去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去進行擴張
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.65,0:12:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈 日記
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.09,0:12:32.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈 日記
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.11,0:12:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過還真是偶然呢 加奈也去擴張
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.08,0:12:42.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起偶然 其實是代理…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.96,0:12:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈 妳和她一起去擴張
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.60,0:12:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後妳在她旁邊微笑 明白了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.23,0:12:54.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 但是我的笑臉還…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:57.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個笑臉會成為強力的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:13:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,強力的武器 我的笑臉不是還不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.27,0:13:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 妳的笑臉非常棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.61,0:13:09.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好的笑臉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.34,0:13:13.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我果然是行的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 所以幹勁十足的去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.07,0:13:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.08,0:13:22.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 那麼說加奈也要跟我去同一個地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.68,0:13:23.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.44,0:13:30.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擴張原來是同別的專賣所的人一同工作的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我按咯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.41,0:13:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.39,0:13:44.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要訂花日報紙嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.06,0:13:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久地院同學這樣不行啊 這個人是外國人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.00,0:13:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 花日報紙？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.81,0:13:53.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能聽懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:14:00.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 我是風新報紙 請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.06,0:14:03.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,NO~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.52,0:14:06.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.29,0:14:09.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 下一家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.32,0:14:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.39,0:14:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是花日報紙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.65,0:14:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是風新報紙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.03,0:14:21.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要訂報紙麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…久地院同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.69,0:14:33.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.92,0:14:37.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.71,0:14:45.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一家！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.80,0:14:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來 嚇跑的客人讓小遙去簽回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.06,0:15:06.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全軍覆沒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.27,0:15:08.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.29,0:15:10.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會這樣呢 久地院同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.88,0:15:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想問啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.96,0:15:18.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不太明白 但大家好像是看到加奈的臉後就把門關上的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.78,0:15:20.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.61,0:15:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是但是 代理說我的笑臉很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是大家一看到我的臉就把門關了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.18,0:15:31.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 這是為什麼呢 咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.32,0:15:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 真是個喋喋不休的煩人傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.97,0:15:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我看看 加奈的那個笑臉讓我看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.99,0:15:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…我笑了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.24,0:15:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.96,0:15:55.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.31,0:15:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那笑臉很糟糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.50,0:16:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 果然很糟糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.27,0:16:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:03.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.87,0:16:09.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 那麼變為不糟糕的笑臉不就可以了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,練習 練習笑容的話就會好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.34,0:16:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久地院同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:22.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 代理也跟我說要靠練習
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.72,0:16:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那麼讓我幫助妳練習也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.77,0:16:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:30.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說過妳可以依靠我的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.52,0:16:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太感謝了 美華醬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.63,0:16:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美華…醬？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:44.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 別叫得這樣輕浮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.12,0:16:48.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 美…久地院同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不覺就 哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.60,0:16:56.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.55,0:16:57.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.36,0:17:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.31,0:17:02.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 我覺得是非常棒的笑臉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.93,0:17:07.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那是當然 好了 加奈也試著做做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:08.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:09.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.09,0:17:10.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛太瞇了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.43,0:17:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.55,0:17:14.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這回睜太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這回怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.98,0:17:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.05,0:17:17.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.50,0:17:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:24.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.51,0:17:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底哪點沒做好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.27,0:17:37.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經不知道如何是好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是太僵硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.53,0:17:45.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要亂動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久地院同學 好癢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.37,0:17:50.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說了不要亂動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 還算可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.06,0:18:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.94,0:18:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 已經不是很糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:15.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我們出陣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.38,0:18:21.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在家吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.63,0:18:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,電表在轉 肯定在家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.78,0:18:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,豈有此理 看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.05,0:18:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣做不行的啊 要被罵的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.03,0:18:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎麼做好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.55,0:18:41.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.02,0:18:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢吞吞的 既然這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.82,0:18:49.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,著火啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.63,0:18:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,著火了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,著火？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,著火？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪著火了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:57.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒地方著火 只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:18:59.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:08.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚇死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嚇死了 讓好不容易到手的機會跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:12.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.61,0:19:16.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,練習的結果 展示加奈笑容的機會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:22.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 好不容易久地院同學那麼努力地幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.66,0:19:24.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我卻逃跑了 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:27.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼蠢話 竟然說我是為了妳什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.80,0:19:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經8點了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.74,0:19:32.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不快點回去的話 大家一定要擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.79,0:19:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.97,0:19:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.28,0:19:40.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.54,0:19:45.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.97,0:19:56.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈 從今以後叫我名也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.16,0:19:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.08,0:20:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我心胸寬廣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道了 美華醬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.03,0:20:07.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈那個傢伙 明明可以笑出那麼燦爛的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.44,0:20:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說起來 我今天做了笑容的練習哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.32,0:20:32.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑容的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.56,0:20:33.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,練習嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.64,0:20:40.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣的 加奈的擴張笑容真的很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.98,0:20:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太過分了 不要哭 加奈醬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.21,0:20:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 對不起 糟糕的是這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.41,0:20:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係的 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.17,0:20:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.82,0:20:55.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為此我努力的練習了的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.85,0:20:59.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就讓我們看看練習的成果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.95,0:21:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我要笑了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.13,0:21:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Smile
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.81,0:21:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？ 我有什麼不對勁的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.24,0:21:27.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 比起白天那個 進步了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.46,0:21:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.86,0:21:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 到底是什麼樣的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:33.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Smile
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.17,0:21:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是變的相當不錯了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:41.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈醬 真的太可愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.86,0:21:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婆婆 我和大家在一起感覺非常開心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.22,0:23:33.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 第一次的、游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.34,0:23:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要玩點心的接詞遊戲咯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.04,0:23:37.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,yo 優酪乳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.63,0:23:38.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,to 巧克力糖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.66,0:23:39.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,fu 麩果子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.00,0:23:42.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,si 鹹牛奶糖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.23,0:23:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,RU~~RU~~
